Text: Hey come on people. I know how many have downloaded this in the past, there were 23 seeders at one time. If you get it for free, share it for free. Don't hog the goods people, share the wealth.
Ohh, here is another thought, how about the seeders we do have, kick up their upload limit to, let's say, UNLIMITED, so I'm not stuck at 3KB/s download from 6 people.
